para_trans: Mauje Jogeshwari, Ta. Regarding sanction of Primary Health Centre at Gangapur, ZP Sambhajinagar.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.111 / Health-4

Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai: J. No. S. A. / Room-7A / T-8 / Jogeshwari / Pre-Centre / Establishment / G. Sambhajinagar / 1245-47/2024, d. 04.03.2024.
Preface: Mouje Jogeshwari, Ta. Health issues to the citizens of the area of Gangapur, ZP Sambhajinagar
A new primary health centre is required to be sanctioned in connection with the provision of facilities at the site.
The issue of sanctioning a primary health centre was under the consideration of the government. The decisions in this regard are as follows:
Government Decision: - Mauje Jogeshwari, Ta. New Primary Health Centre at Gangapur, G.S. Sambhajinagar as a "Special Case"
2. Acquisition of space for this Primary Health Centre in the prescribed manner at the site of the Primary Health Centre.
Separate action on construction of health centre, post creation from district planning fund
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
